Rudyard Kipling's The Jungle Book;;55;;80;;PG;;When his father is killed by a jungle tiger, Mowgli (Jason Scott Lee) is orphaned and grows up in the wild, raised by animals. Years later, the bracelet given to him by his childhood friend, Kitty (Lena Headey), is stolen. In pursuing it, he discovers Monkey City with all its treasures. He is reunited with Kitty, but struggles to adapt to civilization. When Kitty's unscrupulous suitor, Capt. Boone (Cary Elwes), attempts to raid the jungle of its treasures, Mowgli's life is imperiled.;;Romance,Adventure,Kids & family;;Stephen Sommers;;1994;;Jason Scott Lee,Cary Elwes,Lena Headey,Sam Neill,John Cleese,Jason Flemyng,Stefan Kalipha,Ron Donachie;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1057637-jungle_book